To clone a repository:
git clone https://github.com/robingreig/raspi-git

1) To check the status of any local changes
	git status

2) To add the changes to the Index:
	git add <filename>
	git add * ... or git add -A

3) To commit the changes to the HEAD, but not the remote repository yet:
	git commit -m "Commit Message"

4) Pushing the changes to the master:
	git push origin master

5) To sync the master back to raspi
	git pull

good website: rogerdudler.github.io/git-guide



